《'''Love & Hate'''》是[[韓國|韓國]][[女歌手|女歌手]][[金孝靜|孝琳]]（韓國[[女子組合|女子組合]][[SISTAR|SISTAR]]隊長）的首張正規專輯，由[[STARSHIP娛樂|STARSHIP娛樂]]於2013年11月26日發行。

== 發行 ==
2013年11月26日，孝琳正式個人出道，推出首張正規專輯《Love & Hate》<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/34494?fb_comment_id=549390091806156_3674317#f9000e54dc8b24|title= SISTAR孝琳眾望所歸的SOLO出輯！|date= 2013-11-19|accessdate= 2013-11-19|work= 韓星網|language= zh|archive-date= 2016-11-12|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161112145014/http://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/34494?fb_comment_id=549390091806156_3674317#f9000e54dc8b24|dead-url= no}}</ref>，收錄十首的歌曲，部份歌曲由著名作曲家[[勇敢兄弟|勇敢兄弟]]、[[二段橫踢|二段橫踢]]等人作曲。孝琳亦在專輯中，與[[Mad_Clown|Mad Clown]]、[[Dok2|Dok2]]和[[Zico_(歌手)|Zico]]合作<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.allkpop.com/article/2013/11/hyorin-unveils-tracklist-for-upcoming-solo-album-love-hate#ixzz2lACDJAU6|title= Hyorin unveils tracklist for upcoming solo album 'LOVE & HATE'|date= 2013-11-20|accessdate= 2013-11-20|work= allkpop.com|language= en|archive-date= 2020-03-20|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200320013902/https://www.allkpop.com/article/2013/11/hyorin-unveils-tracklist-for-upcoming-solo-album-love-hate#ixzz2lACDJAU6|dead-url= no}}</ref>。此專輯在[[Gaon_Chart|Gaon Chart]]網站的每周專輯榜中，獲得第五名<ref name=gaon-lpwk>{{cite web |url= http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/chart/album.php?f_chart_kind_cd=T&f_week=49&f_year=2013&f_type=week |title= 2013년 49주차 Album Chart |work= Gaon Chart |publisher= Korea Music Content Industry Association |accessdate= 2014-07-26 |language= Ko |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141015003544/http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/chart/album.php?f_chart_kind_cd=T&f_week=49&f_year=2013&f_type=week |archive-date= 2014-10-15 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。

雙主打歌曲之一的「Lonely」的MV遠赴[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]取景拍攝，MV於2013年11月25日正式公開。「Lonely」一曲在[[Billboard|Billboard]]排行榜中獲得第五位，在Gaon單曲週榜中則得第三位<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.allkpop.com/article/2013/11/sistars-hyorin-sings-about-being-lonely-in-new-mv |title= SISTAR's Hyorin sings about being 'Lonely' in new MV! |publisher= allkpop.com |date= 2013-11-25 |accessdate= 2013-11-25 |language= en |archive-date= 2018-01-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180108162152/https://www.allkpop.com/article/2013/11/sistars-hyorin-sings-about-being-lonely-in-new-mv |dead-url= no }}</ref>。另外一首的主打歌曲「One Way Love」的MV由[[柳演錫|柳演錫]]擔任男主角<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.allkpop.com/article/2013/11/hyorin-knows-its-one-way-love-in-new-mv#axzz2ldP8LXFL|title= Hyorin thinks it's 'One Way Love' in new MV|date= 2013-11-26|accessdate= 2013-11-26|work= allkpop.com|language= en|archive-date= 2020-03-20|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200320013854/https://www.allkpop.com/article/2013/11/hyorin-knows-its-one-way-love-in-new-mv#axzz2ldP8LXFL|dead-url= no}}</ref>，在Gaon單曲週榜和[[Billboard|Billboard]]排行榜中皆獲得第一位<ref name=gaon-1wl>{{cite web|title=2013년 49주차 Digital Chart|url=http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=49&hitYear=2013&termGbn=week|website=Gaon|accessdate=2015-02-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208013706/http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=49&hitYear=2013&termGbn=week|archivedate=2015-02-08|language=ko|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

同日，孝琳在[[首爾|首爾]][[江南區_(首爾)|江南區]]清潭洞舉行專輯發行紀念公演<ref>{{cite web |url= http://news.naver.com/main/read.nhn?mode=LSD&mid=sec&sid1=103&oid=014&aid=0003033374 |title= 씨스타 효린 솔로가수 데뷔..가요계 지각변동 |publisher= naver.com |date= 2013-11-25 |accessdate= 2013-11-25 |language= ko |archive-date= 2013-12-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131202233619/http://news.naver.com/main/read.nhn?mode=LSD&mid=sec&sid1=103&oid=014&aid=0003033374 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。她於[[Mnet|Mnet]]的紀念公演上演唱《Love & Hate》內的歌曲，亦聯同其他[[SISTAR|SISTAR]]成員表演她們的歌曲。過往只有[[BoA|BoA]]、[[李孝利|李孝利]]和[[Rain|Rain]]等明星才能於[[Mnet|Mnet]]上進行紀念公演<ref>{{cite web|url= http://mwave.interest.me/mnettv/videodetail.m?searchVideoDetailVO.clip_id=159047|title= Mnet Special- HyoLyn's Love & Hate|work= Mnet|date= 2013-11-26|accessdate= 2013-11-26|language= en|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131204055454/http://mwave.interest.me/mnettv/videodetail.m?searchVideoDetailVO.clip_id=159047|archive-date= 2013-12-04|dead-url= yes}}</ref>。

